Trump ya yi jawabi a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai yi jawabi a cikin jerin jawabai a wannan dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin taro biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake dakatar da zaben tabbatar da dan takararsa a kan wata kujera da ta rage a kotun koli, Trump na son ya kara samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa kujerar 'yan majalisa a zaben Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a fara wasan kwaikwayo na Trump a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi magana ne a kan shari'ar da aka yi wa dan takararsa na kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi babban jarabawar a wannan makon, a kan zarginsa da yin lalata da shi, kuma ana sa ran cewa za a dage kuri'ar amincewa da shi a majalisar dattijai nan da mako guda, kafin a fara binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu ci gaba kafin zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labaran Reuters, masu shirya kamfen din shugaba Trump sun ce taron na mako biyar da ke tafe na nufin "ba da kwarin gwiwa ga masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya, domin 'yan Republican su yi kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai".
"Gwamnatin majalisar dattijai na da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa na neman shugaban kasa, saboda haka zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a wannan lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kungiyar Trump, wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba.
A wani rahoto da gidan rediyon West Virginia Metro News ya fitar, an yi hasashen cewa masu goyon baya daga jihohin Ohio da Pennsylvania za su halarci taron a filin wasa na Wesbank a Wheeling, kuma 'yan jaridu daga Pittsburgh za su iya kallon taron.
A ranar Asabar, za a yi ziyarar ta biyu a watan da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, inda ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na jam'iyyar Republican daga jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke fama da karancin kuri'a a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa dole ne shugaban ya zo ya taimaka masa a binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
