Turai ta samu nasara a gasar Ryder Cup ta yau, bayan da ta yi nasara a wasan biyu da aka yi ranar Asabar da ci 10 da 6 a kan Amurka.
Ƙwararrun 'yan wasa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, waɗanda aka ce sun kusan lashe Tiger Woods sau biyu, sun yanke shawarar yin nasara a Le Golf National.
Tauraron Turai da Thomas Bjorn, wanda ya yi niyyar ci gaba da lashe kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya yi fice a wasannin farko da aka buga da kwallaye biyu da 'yan wasan Amurka, wadanda suka yi kasa a wasan 3-1.
