Sun sami nasara 2&1 a kan Spaniya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan kwallon kafa biyu, kuma sun dawo daga baya don kayar da Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan biyu, duk da cewa ya buga ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup, wata kungiya ta koma daga rashin nasara da maki hudu a wasan farko, duk da cewa a matsayin kungiyar Furyk mai kare ta bukaci kwallo daya ne kawai domin ta lashe kofin.
