Tauraruwar wasan kwaikwayo na "Game of Thrones" Kit Harington ya shiga cikin wani hali na maza mai guba
Kit Harington ya shahara a matsayin Jon Snow da takobi a cikin wani mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na tsakiya.
Amma dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi watsi da ra'ayin da ake da shi na jarumin jarumi, ya ce irin wannan rawar da ake yi a kan allon na nuna cewa matasa maza suna jin cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsaurin kai don a girmama su.
Kit Culture ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa ya yi imanin cewa "wani abu ba daidai ba ne" kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar ƙwayoyin maza masu guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri tauraronsa a Star of Thrones, Rose Leslie, shi ma mai shekara 31, ya ce yana da "ra'ayin da ya dace" game da wannan batun.
"A wannan lokacin, ni kaina ina jin, da karfi sosai - menene ya faru da ya zama mummunan hali ga maza?" in ji shi.
'Mene ne muke koya wa matasa maza game da matsalar da muke fuskanta a yau?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na alhakin hauhawar cutar maza saboda yadda ake nuna maza a cikinta.
Ya ci gaba, "Abin da aka haifa da abin da aka koya?
Me ake koya wa yara maza a talabijin, a kan titi, da su yi tunanin cewa kowane namiji yana da wani bangare na kansa?
Ina ganin wannan shi ne ainihin babbar tambayar zamaninmu - yaya za mu sauya wannan?
Domin wani abu ya canza ga wani saurayi mafi muni.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani prequel ko kuma wasa ba Game of Thrones bayan kammala wasan kwaikwayo, saboda yana da isasshen fights da dawakai.
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi wasa a fim mai suna Sam Shepard's True West, wanda ke magana game da wani mai yin fim da kuma ɗan'uwansa ɗan fashi.
