Kakakin gwamnatin ya ce: Mun tsara ingantaccen tsari na yadda za mu yi hulda da EU nan gaba.
Taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya sake jinkirta, in ji Fadar White House
Babban taron Donald Trump da babban lauya Janar Rod Rosenstein na iya jinkirta zuwa mako guda saboda ci gaba da fafatawa tsakanin Brett Kavanaugh da Alkalin Kotun Duniya, Fadar White House ta sanar a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana sa ido kan ayyukan kwamitin musamman na Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma baki a zaben Rasha, alaƙar da ke tsakanin masu goyon bayan Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban shiga shari'a.
Ko da Trump ya kori babban jami'in da ke wakiltarsa, kuma ya yi barazanar 'yancin Mueller, Washington ta yi ta yin jita-jita da wannan batun na tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ce Rosenstein ya tattauna batun amfani da kyamarori wajen yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump ya yi da kuma yiwuwar kawar da shugaban kasa ta hanyar gyaran doka na 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta cewa ya yi hakan.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya shiga fadar White House cike da rahotanni cewa yana shirin yin murabus.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da taron da za a yi ranar Alhamis da Trump, wanda a lokacin yana a hedikwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce ba zai kori Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka jinkirta ganawar don kada ta kai ga sauraron kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai, inda aka gabatar da shaidar Kavanaugh da kuma wata mace da ta zargi shi da lalata da ita, Dakta Christine Blasey Ford.
A ranar Juma'a ne Trump ya umarci FBI da ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan tuhumar da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya sake jinkirta zaman majalisar dattawa.
Kakakin Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a cikin wani rahoto da Fox News ta fitar a ranar Lahadi.
Da aka tambaye ta ko za ta gana da Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a sa ranar ba, amma za a iya yin hakan a wannan makon, kuma za a iya yin hakan a mako mai zuwa saboda sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a kotun koli.
