Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonisiya
Aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta auku a birnin Palu, a ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma hukumomi sun ce ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, rundunar ba ta iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala, yankin da ke arewacin Pallu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga Palos bayan da bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma masarautar Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke a ƙarshen ƙanƙarar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma an kiyasta yawan jama'arta ya kai 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwa sa'ad da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa.
Donggala ita ce masarautar da ke da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yankin da ke ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Babban bangaren tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi na Tsakiya shine kamun kifi da noman, musamman a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Akwai kuma wani babban ma'adinai na nickel a lardin, amma ya fi mayar da hankali a Morowali a gabar tsibirin Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, sun yi tsunami sau da yawa a birnin Palu da Donggal.
Tsunami da ya auku a shekara ta 1938 a Donggale ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a 1996 inda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma a kai a kai ana girgizar ƙasa.
Ga jerin wasu manyan girgizar asa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gabar tekun lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra, a ƙasar Indonisiya, ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin waɗanda suka mutu a lardin Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar tekun Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin lamba 6.8 ta afka wa tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya kashe kusan mutane 700 a gaɓar teku.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin maki 7.6 ta auku a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin maki 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 30 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane wajen 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfi ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, inda ya haifar da halaka da fargaba, yayin da mutane suka tuna da mummunar tasirin girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004 .
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sanadiyyar rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawa a bangaren arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido suka makale.
