Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yanke hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York sun nemi a yanke wa Sayfulla Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas. Wannan hukunci ne na musamman, wanda ba a taba yankewa wani babban laifi a jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, a watan Oktoba, an ce ya kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen West Side Highway a cikin Lower Manhattan, ta amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da masu hawa keke fashi.
Don su sami damar yanke hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci a tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi niyyar kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi niyyar cutar da mutane da yawa. Wannan shi ne abin da aka tsara a cikin takardar da kotun ta amince da shi a Kudancin New York.
A cewar bayanan da aka samu a kotu, duka wadannan lambobi biyu za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
A makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da aikata laifuka 22, da suka hada da tuhumar kisa don neman kudi, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokuta masu aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar aikata mugunta da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "babban shiri da shiri", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan aika-aika a matsayin "mai ban tsoro, da mugunta, da kuma ta'asa".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholaus Clevese, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlija, Hernán Ferruchi, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnucca rauni, azaba da asara,an ambaci sunansa da gangan.
