A karshe an kashe mutum a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953, inda aka kashe ma'auratan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, wadanda aka tabbatar sun yi makirci don leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Cacar Baki shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
